{"tid":1388613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(缺人)需要手足黎機場過夜！連續幾日做「和你飛」！","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T05:36:35.000Z","uid":254330,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a71c47c665ab23359ee5a42956bf19a5adddad56","tid":1388613,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:36:42.000Z","msg":"機場唔夠人，要人一齊黎接機！做「和你飛」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知聽日大家仲有好多地方要去，但係請抽少少時間黎一黎機場，咩。未必要係聽日，可以係遲幾日！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊比海外旅客知道香港發生緊咩事！<br />\n<br />\n請盡量抽少少人出黎一齊接力！我地嘅目標係機場令海外旅客知道<span style=\"color: red;\">香港政府、警察同支那國嘅暴行</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">比壓力政府</span>，我地希望能夠活動可以延續到8月5號大罷工果日，係8月5號令更多人入機場，比海外旅客睇清楚真正嘅香港人係點樣嘅！<br />\n<br />\n今日有好多巴絲都捐左唔少物資黎機場！非常感謝你地！<br />\n但係我地唔夠人接力出去<span style=\"color: red;\">接機+守物資+休息</span>！要人黎接力！今晚得6個人留左係機場，仲要分工睇物資、接機同休息，有巴打已經企左12個鐘，啱啱先坐低休息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DBEoD6U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDBEoD6U.png&h=11b7a1f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D9zHadA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD9zHadA.png&h=88b1cf41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留係現場嘅有3個係需要助養嘅兒童！<br />\n<br />\n另外我地物資充足，加上機場要食野買野其實好方便，帶個水樽黎，係機場水任斟，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再帶水</span>黎機場物資站喇！毛巾、食物都足夠，黎接力嘅巴打最好自己帶插頭+差電線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n建議搞多次「和你飛」集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n係到留左名嘅巴絲記得抽1、2日出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0d93a6183f5b6aad52d556db43357dc72c16b3","tid":1388613,"uid":254330,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要人接機！"},{"pid":"99dea93a9ea853dcacf7d0e0da3d67e2ba6244eb","tid":1388613,"uid":254330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:38:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\nLiberate Hong Kong<br />\nRevolution of Times<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命 <br />\n</div></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d95629608b50c7bb77f3eed25ee16721f4b8c2cd","tid":1388613,"uid":254330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355e755edec089710f387d4e1b41d94b1403f01b","tid":1388613,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:46:08.000Z","msg":"帶多個口罩比自己！"},{"pid":"977a3a435eeaffe2542612f08d89dd09cc2036ac","tid":1388613,"uid":11964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:47:45.000Z","msg":"加油 幫推"},{"pid":"4511023be99ee77e433ec81f265cc008eadfc1d6","tid":1388613,"uid":278395,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:49:05.000Z","msg":"支持 覺得機場真係幾好既集合地點<br />\n<br />\n但真心建議要吸取之前包圍稅局既經驗(我發夢見到現場情況)<br />\n第1次做成功，當時夠人而且係新方法<br />\n但到第2次效果差好遠，唔夠人堵塞唔到，再加做得太密，無左noise<br />\n<br />\n所以一係唔做 要做就做大做好佢<br />\nThey cant kill us all<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92a48624a7be45e434f76988716123e72daa36c","tid":1388613,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"做得太密留得太耐就會膠化 <br />\n參考雨革"},{"pid":"7e64f3b09a45ecb9d9bf909af8cc605828145f88","tid":1388613,"uid":274475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:51:54.000Z","msg":"Po主有冇evaluate下今日成個下晏完全冇行動? <br />\n<br />\n幾十個手足入左去，冇指示冇野做，聽明星唱歌做show，唔知做乜。"},{"pid":"8dc67632404482477f0332517e4b2a4896f10f4d","tid":1388613,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECZWZks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECZWZks.png&h=38683d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FU1ROdN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFU1ROdN.png&h=788ac637&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPkvjks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPkvjks.png&h=0a389300&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a28ca3ed03d40208db4bbb188a0019e13a0ded81","tid":1388613,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:53:36.000Z","msg":"俾大家參考下Post主響TG呼籲大家嘅守則:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">HK730登機位：T1 接機附近，認識朋友後各自參觀機場或睇戲食野<br />\n<br />\n今日守則：<br />\n 1. 不遊行集會，純玩純參觀<br />\n 2. 不叫口號，不派傳單，不舉牌<br />\n 3. 不能大量人聚集同一個位 be water<br />\n 4. 不能坐定定地下<br />\n 5. 暫時物資充足，不能收取任何金錢/物資<br />\n 6. 請跟從機場保安指示，盡量配合，冷靜應對，保安都是善意的，保安離開後，可做返你既野<br />\n 7. 不接受訪問，除非你想介紹香港機場吃喝玩樂<br />\n 8. 機場有得睇獅子王<br />\n<br />\n今日純粹入機場參觀遊玩，參加者請跟從指示<br />\n<br />\n實時消息：<a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=3f84993e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n慶幸我夜晚出返葵涌。"},{"pid":"5765e06c1279ab8bbbdef409554be7990667b800","tid":1388613,"uid":5172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"聽日放工嚟幫手<br />\n<br />\n利申：機場返工<br />\n公司有得沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa767b260388ecb4f50e273ebe279a2fc134a5a","tid":1388613,"uid":126875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:58:37.000Z","msg":"push!!!"},{"pid":"d431d0031623b30bdbed1659efd9cb4bb9417510","tid":1388613,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1094884e38a04d7092b3cc60c9dbb612a19eba4f","tid":1388613,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c92a48624a7be45e434f76988716123e72daa36c","tid":1388613,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"做得太密留得太耐就會膠化 <br />\n參考雨革"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"我地唔係要佔領 只係接機 <br />\n唔會麻煩任何人 包括機場保安、要去旅行嘅人、機場staff<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440900fb5c0d9bf785203c8a92a38b2764218a64","tid":1388613,"uid":230836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a71c47c665ab23359ee5a42956bf19a5adddad56","tid":1388613,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:36:42.000Z","msg":"機場唔夠人，要人一齊黎接機！做「和你飛」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知聽日大家仲有好多地方要去，但係請抽少少時間黎一黎機場，咩。未必要係聽日，可以係遲幾日！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊比海外旅客知道香港發生緊咩事！<br />\n<br />\n請盡量抽少少人出黎一齊接力！我地嘅目標係機場令海外旅客知道<span style=\"color: red;\">香港政府、警察同支那國嘅暴行</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">比壓力政府</span>，我地希望能夠活動可以延續到8月5號大罷工果日，係8月5號令更多人入機場，比海外旅客睇清楚真正嘅香港人係點樣嘅！<br />\n<br />\n今日有好多巴絲都捐左唔少物資黎機場！非常感謝你地！<br />\n但係我地唔夠人接力出去<span style=\"color: red;\">接機+守物資+休息</span>！要人黎接力！今晚得6個人留左係機場，仲要分工睇物資、接機同休息，有巴打已經企左12個鐘，啱啱先坐低休息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https